data.description: Hurry! This one won't last long!  Gorgeous Contemporary Home is in the highly sought after ''The Bluffs II'' Community! Perfect 3 bed, 2 bath floorplan with an Open Great Room, High Ceilings, a Chef's Kitchen boasting lots of Cabinets and Granite Counter space, plus Breakfast Nook. The Spacious Owner's En-Suite has a Bonus Room for Den, Office, 4th Bedroom, Gym, Nursery, Craft Room, etc. Low Maintenance. Spacious Backyard. Close to Walking/Bike Paths, Schools, Medical, Dining and Shopping! Save on utilities with Leased Solar!
